data.description: HUGE Price Improvement!! Charming, hard to find home in this price range! Covered front porch welcomes you home, nice sized living room, and fenced backyard with a shed. Single car garage with double car carport & driveway. Fridge & Security System with cameras stay. Current entry level home or investment property. Easy access to highways & shopping. Roof replaced around 2018 & updated water heater. A little elbow grease will really make this one shine!
